    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "So I've copied all of the matching flags from `test` to the `Config` file, swapping kebab for snake case, e.g., `--match-test` is `match_test` in `foundry.toml`.\r\n\r\nProfiles work so you can store different matching setups in the config file and select them with `FOUNDRY_PROFILE`\r\n\r\nIf *both* config entry and flag are present, the flag takes precedence. \r\n\r\nThe full list:\r\n\r\n```\r\nmatch_test\r\nno_match_test\r\nmatch_contract\r\nno_match_contract\r\nmatch_path\r\nno_match_path\r\n```\r\n\r\n",
